{"tid":625304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"KMB app 廣告令人反感","createTime":"2018-04-11T10:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T10:34:54.000Z","uid":69901,"like":57,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2df1c48ea32adbb35ca042ba4cb6fd94b06c1079","tid":625304,"uid":69901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:34:54.000Z","msg":"最近 KMB app 一開就有廣告，要自己禁交叉，已經覺得好煩。 今日仲要有廣告video，要睇幾秒先有個細到粒米咁既交叉。<br />\n<br />\nIn-app google banner ads 都算。咁樣完全影響user experience（個app 唔好用都算）。公營機構咁樣賺錢又唔見會減價。<br />\n<br />\n同cs投訴左，但跟本冇用。我相信唔只我不滿，大家圍下爐，或者意識到有問題，就是改變的第一步。"},{"pid":"01a1720514d84b82297af27f6c4b3531e3752d5e","tid":625304,"uid":21423,"like":12,"dislike":10,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:41:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9c0717eb54c7fb8dc865bdfa1f985f077d9f20b","tid":625304,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:42:29.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n以後有新線招標<br />\n全力支持城巴中標"},{"pid":"acc3b6d1e25d17d30df6b772f4fe37d51c155d8d","tid":625304,"uid":181478,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:49:42.000Z","msg":"明~ 樓主係廣告 marketing 想叫人去睇多D"},{"pid":"90d058582988dfa7d1f426073df831bb580360c4","tid":625304,"uid":29014,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:50:37.000Z","msg":"點止app廣告令人反感<br />\n我搭成程車對住隻灰甲真係飯都唔撚想食<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/185034_11dab884073e83780f5817639ec31a94.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F185034_11dab884073e83780f5817639ec31a94.png&h=8ad93504&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cdb0151f3c9871fa3c86dca4cccf324408a5fb2","tid":625304,"uid":2442,"like":1,"dislike":26,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:53:14.000Z","msg":"痴線，我想check 下巴士重有幾耐啫，入左apps 一片空白，等左一陣原來load 緊廣告，唸住close左佢，搵離搵去都唔知邊到close，求其click，點鬼知佢link 左去廣告，彈左去safari，我部舊iphone 勁慢，等一陣先load 到safari，我即刻close 左，轉番去九巴apps，唸住seaech 巴士号碼，<img src=\"/assets/f